{"tid":2136051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【快訊】路透社：TikTok 同意出售給微軟","createTime":"2020-08-01T20:56:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T23:24:41.000Z","uid":9031,"like":8,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e509246908b135875232a97736f086b0e25507b8","tid":2136051,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T20:56:16.000Z","msg":"TikTok 母公司字節跳動終於同意完全剝離 TikTok 在美國的業務，並出售給微軟。<br />\n<br />\n根據路透社報導，在美國總統川普宣布要禁止 TikTok 在美國營運之後，TikTok 母公司字節跳動（ByteDance）終於同意完全剝離 TikTok 在美國的業務，並出售給微軟，目前 TikTok 在美國有超過 8,000 萬名活躍使用者。<br />\n<br />\n先前字節跳動早已同意出售，但希望保留部分股權，但被白宮拒絕了。根據新的交易條件， 字節跳動將完全退出，微軟公司將接管美國的 TikTok，並掌握 TikTok 所有美國使用者的資料。<br />\n<br />\n不過白宮並未對此交易發表評論，川普於昨日仍然不傾向於同意 TikTok 的交易，而微軟與北京的字節跳動同樣不願發表評論。"},{"pid":"55629e0144b0846801abfbcebdbfb3531f154cfd","tid":2136051,"uid":10606,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T20:56:36.000Z","msg":"星期一Allin MSFT"},{"pid":"41ac41bb93a5806547c6342ca44a33316eb4be49","tid":2136051,"uid":154486,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T21:00:33.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>微軟已經停左<br />\nput on hold</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/microsoft-and-bytedance-put-tiktok-talks-on-hold-after-trump-signals-opposition-11596312611\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fmicrosoft-and-bytedance-put-tiktok-talks-on-hold-after-trump-signals-opposition-11596312611&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnf5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=1b99d236\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/microsoft-and-bytedance-put-tiktok-talks-on-hold-after-trump-signals-opposition-11596312611</a><br />\n<br />\n侵反對"},{"pid":"e0a5857f3cc860c5c51db7a0e556af78dc3e742c","tid":2136051,"uid":4783,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"41ac41bb93a5806547c6342ca44a33316eb4be49","tid":2136051,"uid":154486,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T21:00:33.00